title: Locals offered more choices to buy New Zealand properties
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Locals offered more choices to buy Ne... Locals offered more choices to buy New Zealand properties Next Story Prev Story 2 hrs ago Read more: Daily Express 
Kota Kinabalu: Property buyers in the city now have more choices to own properties in New Zealand with All Property Solution's Queens Square luxury apartments in Auckland. The luxury apartments which consists of 226 superior freehold strata title residences and nine boutique retail shops is located on Queen Street - Auckland's premier shopping and entertainment precinct - the equivalent of Shanghai's Nanjing Road or Singapore's Orchard Road, or Kuala Lumpur's Bukit Bintang.
